{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "HowTo",
  "name": "HOW TO TITLE (e.g., How to Optimize Your Website for AI)",
  "description": "Brief overview of what this guide teaches and what readers will accomplish",
  "image": {
    "@type": "ImageObject",
    "url": "https://www.yourwebsite.com/how-to-guide-image.jpg",
    "height": 406,
    "width": 305
  },
  "totalTime": "PT30M",
  "estimatedCost": {
    "@type": "MonetaryAmount",
    "currency": "USD",
    "value": "0"
  },
  "supply": [
    {
      "@type": "HowToSupply",
      "name": "Computer or laptop"
    },
    {
      "@type": "HowToSupply",
      "name": "Website access"
    },
    {
      "@type": "HowToSupply",
      "name": "Text editor or CMS"
    }
  ],
  "tool": [
    {
      "@type": "HowToTool",
      "name": "Google Search Console"
    },
    {
      "@type": "HowToTool",
      "name": "Schema validator"
    }
  ],
  "step": [
    {
      "@type": "HowToStep",
      "name": "Step 1 Title",
      "text": "Detailed instructions for the first step. Be clear and specific about what to do.",
      "url": "https://www.yourwebsite.com/guide#step1",
      "image": "https://www.yourwebsite.com/step1-image.jpg"
    },
    {
      "@type": "HowToStep",
      "name": "Step 2 Title",
      "text": "Instructions for the second step. Include any important details or warnings.",
      "url": "https://www.yourwebsite.com/guide#step2",
      "image": "https://www.yourwebsite.com/step2-image.jpg"
    },
    {
      "@type": "HowToStep",
      "name": "Step 3 Title",
      "text": "Third step instructions. Break complex tasks into manageable sub-steps.",
      "url": "https://www.yourwebsite.com/guide#step3",
      "image": "https://www.yourwebsite.com/step3-image.jpg"
    },
    {
      "@type": "HowToStep",
      "name": "Step 4 Title",
      "text": "Final step instructions. Explain what success looks like and next steps.",
      "url": "https://www.yourwebsite.com/guide#step4",
      "image": "https://www.yourwebsite.com/step4-image.jpg"
    }
  ],
  "yield": "One fully optimized website"
}

<!-- 
INSTRUCTIONS:
1. Include minimum 2 steps (no maximum)
2. Each step should be on your page in the same order
3. Use ISO 8601 duration format for totalTime (see examples below)
4. Include images for steps when possible (improves rich results)
5. URLs in steps can link to anchors on the same page

REQUIRED FIELDS:
- @context, @type, name, step (array with at least 2 steps)
- Each step needs: name, text

RECOMMENDED FIELDS:
- description, image, totalTime, supply, tool

OPTIONAL BUT VALUABLE:
- estimatedCost, yield

TIME DURATION FORMAT (ISO 8601):
- PT30M = 30 minutes
- PT1H = 1 hour
- PT2H30M = 2 hours 30 minutes
- PT45S = 45 seconds
- P1D = 1 day
- P2DT3H = 2 days 3 hours

STEP VARIATIONS:

Simple step (minimum required):
{
  "@type": "HowToStep",
  "name": "Step name",
  "text": "Step instructions"
}

Step with sub-steps (HowToSection):
{
  "@type": "HowToSection",
  "name": "Major section title",
  "itemListElement": [
    {
      "@type": "HowToStep",
      "name": "Sub-step 1",
      "text": "Instructions"
    },
    {
      "@type": "HowToStep",
      "name": "Sub-step 2",
      "text": "Instructions"
    }
  ]
}

Step with direction (HowToDirection):
Can include more detailed directions within a step:
{
  "@type": "HowToStep",
  "name": "Configure settings",
  "itemListElement": [
    {
      "@type": "HowToDirection",
      "text": "Click the Settings menu"
    },
    {
      "@type": "HowToDirection",
      "text": "Select Advanced Options"
    }
  ]
}

ESTIMATED COST EXAMPLES:

Free:
"estimatedCost": {
  "@type": "MonetaryAmount",
  "currency": "USD",
  "value": "0"
}

Range:
"estimatedCost": {
  "@type": "MonetaryAmount",
  "currency": "USD",
  "value": "50",
  "maxValue": "100",
  "minValue": "25"
}

BEST PRACTICES:
- Keep steps in logical order
- Use action verbs to start each step
- Include images or videos when possible
- Be specific about measurements and quantities
- Warn about common mistakes
- Explain why each step matters
- Test your instructions yourself

RICH RESULTS:
HowTo schema can appear as:
- Carousel in search results
- Voice assistant instructions
- AI platform step-by-step guides
- Featured snippets with images
-->
